{"title": "Food delivery riders offering illegal hitch rides on messaging platforms", "tags": "singapore", "timestamp": "2023-06-18", "content": "SINGAPORE \u2013 Food delivery riders are moonlighting and offering illegal hitch rides on messaging platforms, with checks showing more than 10,500 messages in four chat groups on Telegram \u2013 mostly seeking rides.\nThe groups have a total of about 50,000 members, which is about a sixth of the 300,000 members in the nine chat groups on Telegram offering illegal hitch car rides, The Straits Times found."}